claim.claim-text:
1. A Chinese medicine which can prevent and treat cancer, wherein the medicine comprises the following ingredients in weight percentage: 
(a) 20-30% powder of head and neck of soft-shelled turtle; 
(b) 0.05-3% powder of muskiness; 
(c) 5-10% powder of bear gall; 
(d) 20-30% powder of achyranthes root; 
(e) 0.5-3% powder of bitter almond; 
(f) 20-63% powder of black ant; and 
(g) 2-3% powder of rhubarb.
